{"tid":2197954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華盛頓州幼童葬身火海 父母命危  加州山火 百萬公頃變煉獄","createTime":"2020-09-11T04:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T05:32:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"aa717fe18fbdc348bcf8cd1a337a17d9fe6f23fe","tid":2197954,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:12:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200911/LZ2ITYJAX5G4RGG7IORY5XQSCI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200911%2FLZ2ITYJAX5G4RGG7IORY5XQSCI%2F&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=5a509aeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200911%2FLZ2ITYJAX5G4RGG7IORY5XQSCI%2F&h=361f1752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200911/LZ2ITYJAX5G4RGG7IORY5XQSCI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓州幼童葬身火海 父母命危 <br />\n加州山火 百萬公頃變煉獄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yFHRrTLiBF0eyR3btBHPbCRmfkk=/3298x2215/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AEMFBB42AJE6BHH2GC5VOKFYKI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyFHRrTLiBF0eyR3btBHPbCRmfkk%3D%2F3298x2215%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAEMFBB42AJE6BHH2GC5VOKFYKI.jpg&h=0d1400e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■加州奧羅維爾湖上的比德維爾大橋被大火包圍。法新社<br />\n<br />\n美國西岸持續燒了一個月的山火仍未受控制，迄今至少有八人葬身火海。其中加州的火場面積已擴大到破紀錄的100萬公頃，相當於10個香港大小，幾乎是去年同期的10倍。在華盛頓和俄勒岡兩個州的大火又吞噬了多個社區，逾3,500幢房屋焚毀。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：三藩市濃煙蔽日 天色暗橙如火星<br />\n<br />\n救援人員前日找到年紀最小的死者年僅1歲，這位男孩和家人在華盛頓州北部。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s4yNSSkS4a5b3msKmumjUVMgUNA=/1794x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HKHLI6CTXBG4ZI3E4NXZFQUJEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs4yNSSkS4a5b3msKmumjUVMgUNA%3D%2F1794x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHKHLI6CTXBG4ZI3E4NXZFQUJEQ.jpg&h=9642bd6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■消防員在大火面前顯得束手無策。法新社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TDITW_NDDjh19WROz54_6UjrXYc=/1660x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DDJCQHAZDBHVTKWHLI4HQ5I3UA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTDITW_NDDjh19WROz54_6UjrXYc%3D%2F1660x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDDJCQHAZDBHVTKWHLI4HQ5I3UA.jpg&h=cf6be981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■加州比尤特縣有店舖被焚毀。法新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「惡魔風」煽動 火勢急且兇<br />\n<br />\n59歲赫爾是馬爾登鎮災民，過往從事災後重建的生意，即使有豐富經驗，亦未能洞悉天機，及早防範，當日警長挨家挨戶叫人疏散時，他也來不及收拾細軟便要逃生。赫爾的房子最終跟鎮上大部份建築物一樣變成焦炭，他坦言「曾目睹過這種損失破壞不下數十次」，只是沒想過會發生在他自己身上，對一直無為房子購買火災保險感到十分後悔。<br />\n<br />\n受乾燥季候現象「惡魔風」(Diablo Winds)的影響，８、９月向來是加州的山火旺季，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出動1.4萬消防員撲救<br />\n<br />\n加州出動了超過1.4萬名消防員撲救，但火場不斷擴大令他們疲於奔命，三名消防員在中央海岸大蘇爾附近救火時，突然風勢逆轉，一度被困火場，後來各人獲救，傷勢亦無大礙。不少加州人選擇到俄勒岡州、甚至華盛頓州避難，因為傳統上兩地受濕冷氣流保護，這段時間的山火並不會很大，可是今年卻出現反常。<br />\n<br />\n俄勒岡州州長布朗直言災情「史無前例」，她指當地的藍河、底特律、鳳凰、塔。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》/ 美聯社 / 英國《每日電訊報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gjJ-TBEn6svYEb84flt2IUFEwqI=/1107x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SALMWB4EZ5AEJBBYFLPJDA2I5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgjJ-TBEn6svYEb84flt2IUFEwqI%3D%2F1107x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSALMWB4EZ5AEJBBYFLPJDA2I5E.jpg&h=b0c3aee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■國民警衞軍派飛機撤走加州災民。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n=============<br />\n<br />\n睇見呢幅圖即刻諗起捍衛中大幅圖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s4yNSSkS4a5b3msKmumjUVMgUNA=/1794x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HKHLI6CTXBG4ZI3E4NXZFQUJEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs4yNSSkS4a5b3msKmumjUVMgUNA%3D%2F1794x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHKHLI6CTXBG4ZI3E4NXZFQUJEQ.jpg&h=9642bd6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"428d996eae560780a20623c9b7780974fa4c3644","tid":2197954,"uid":143016,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:14:13.000Z","msg":"火燒左膠"},{"pid":"b741f7287fa46e93e0cd4dcaa222a241e5167841","tid":2197954,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:18:49.000Z","msg":"一邊火一邊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022c9e30f6c59798540ca885cc8ed1854bfda7b0","tid":2197954,"uid":127575,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"左膠：我唔知"},{"pid":"c1bb6494188db2794eda421f1eb53a1ba1d454d8","tid":2197954,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:23:30.000Z","msg":"COVID 都未搞掂又超級火災<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter 好多美國人悲觀到覺得審判日/世界末日到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdb83319c858c8e9f5a077b5022191ed799eb9b","tid":2197954,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"成篇野比你貼撚晒咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"